Company Overview
Crio, Inc. produces cocoa and chocolate products. Its products include Crio BrÃ¼ brewed cocoa, Crio beans â€“ chocolate covered cocoa beans, and gourmet hot cocoa. The company sells products through its online store. Crio, Inc. was founded in 2010 and is based in Lindon, Utah.


