Crio Bru Brewed Cocoa


                Tags:
                
                Beverages :: Hot Beverages

Crio Bru is made from a single ingredientâ€”roasted and ground cocoa beans.  Our proprietary harvesting techniques and perfected roasting levels preserve the innate nutritional profile of our beans while unlocking intense and complex flavors.  Crio Bru is brewed like coffee resulting in a healthy, rich, dark chocolate drink that naturally has 0 fat, 0 sugars, just 10 calories, and up to 4x the antioxidants of coffee per 8-oz. serving. Oh, and itâ€™s delicious!

ABOUT THE PRODUCER



Crio Inc.
                            Lindon, UT
                            702-808-4845


Crio Bru is 100% cocoa that brews like coffee.  It is the first product of its kind to market, developed by Eric Durtschi, a founder and officer of Crio Inc.  Crio Beans are organic cocoa beans that have been hand-washed, roasted and covered in a fine dark chocolate.  Crio is only one of two companies in the United States to produce a similar product. Crio plans to launch additional product lines this year-Crio Cocoa Shell Tea, Crio Espresso, Crio Gourmet Hot Coca Mix, etc.





